---
// Pricing section - Outcome-Tied Pricing
---

<section class="pricing-section" id="pricing">
  <div class="pricing-container">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="pricing-header reveal-up">
      <div class="section-badge">Commercial Model</div>
      <h2 class="pricing-title">Outcome-tied pricing</h2>
      <p class="pricing-subtitle">You pay for operational outcomes — not licenses, unused features, or experiments.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pricing Cards -->
    <div class="pricing-cards">
      <!-- Card 1: One-Time Setup Fee -->
      <div class="pricing-card reveal-up">
        <div class="pricing-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pricing-card-title">One-Time Setup Fee</h3>
        <p class="pricing-card-desc">Covers audit, system design, build, and full integration into your existing stack.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Monthly Ongoing Fee -->
      <div class="pricing-card reveal-up">
        <div class="pricing-badge-ongoing">ONGOING</div>
        <div class="pricing-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21.5 2v6h-6M2.5 22v-6h6M2 11.5a10 10 0 0 1 18.8-4.3M22 12.5a10 10 0 0 1-18.8 4.2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pricing-card-title">Monthly Ongoing Fee</h3>
        <p class="pricing-card-desc">Covers monitoring, optimization, support, and reporting. Only while you're running.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Small Note Below Cards -->
    <div class="pricing-note reveal-up">
      <p>We do not charge for generic licenses, unused capabilities, and experimental features.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="pricing-cta-block reveal-up">
      <div class="pricing-cta-label">GET STARTED</div>
      <h3 class="pricing-cta-title">Ready to run real automation?</h3>
      <p class="pricing-cta-desc">RYX AI is suited for organizations that want to run automation in real operations — not experiment with AI. Start with an operational audit conversation.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-pricing-primary">Book a Demo →</a>
      <p class="pricing-cta-note">No commitment. We start by understanding your operations.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
